{{/components-title }}

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="bt-primary" dark="true" do="true" warning="true" dont="true" title="Bouton primaire" desc="Le bouton primaire <code>is-primary</code> est un bouton call-to-action impactant."}}
        {{#content "light"}}
            <div class="buttons">
                <a class="button is-primary">Standard</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-hovered">Hover</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-active">Cliqué</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-focused">Focus</a>
                <a class="button is-primary" disabled="">Inactif</a>
            </div>

            <div class="buttons">
                <a class="button is-primary is-small">Standard</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-small is-hovered">Hover</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-small is-active">Cliqué</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-small is-focused">Focus</a>
            </div>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "dark"}}
            <div class="buttons">
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted">Standard</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-hovered">Hover</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-active">Cliqué</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-focused">Focus</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted" disabled="">Inactif</a>
            </div>

            <div class="buttons">
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-small">Standard</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-small is-hovered">Hover</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-small is-active">Cliqué</a>
                <a class="button is-primary is-inverted is-small is-focused">Focus</a>
            </div>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "do"}}
            <p><em>Voir l'exemple ci-dessus</em></p>

            <ul class="list">
                <li>Pour obtenir un bouton plus petit ajouter la classe <strong class="has-text-primary">.is-small</strong></li>
                <li>Lorsqu'un bouton primaire se trouve dans un bloc à fond coloré, alors il faut lui ajouter la classe <strong class="has-text-primary">.is-inverted</strong>. Le bouton deviendra alors blanc.</li>
            </ul>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "warning"}}
            <p>Voici d'autres boutons existants, mais ils ne doivent <b>pas être utilisés côtés client</b> :</p>

            <div class="buttons is-multiline">
                <a class="button is-info">Button info</a>
                <a class="button is-success">Button success</a>
                <a class="button is-danger">Button danger</a>
                <a class="button is-warning">Button warning</a>
            </div>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "dont"}}
            <ul class="list">
                <li>Trop d'actions dans une page peuvent perdre l'utilisateur</li>
                <li>Ne pas mettre le texte sur deux lignes</li>
            </ul>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}

</section>

